               kpred:has-status   "speculative" ;
               kpred:description  "Inject the Reckons.AI extension into github.com/*/pull/* pages to enable graph browse of a PR. Map changed files -> Codebase KB modules (kpred:has-file), render an inline graph-browse overlay, and surface alignment visually (which planned entities the PR advances/regresses) — the Graph Alignment signal, browsable on the PR. Reuses the extension content-script + sidepanel graph rendering." ;
