               kpred:description  "Reckons.AI uses its own MCP server to track product state. Three internal KBs (Roadmap, Production, Features) symlinked from static/*.ttl into mcp-workspace/kbs/. Claude Code configured via CLAUDE.md + .claude/settings.local.json. Setup: scripts/setup-mcp-workspace.sh." ;
               kpred:depends-on   kb:mcp-server .

